                                </div>
                                <div class="term text-xl mb-1">GTmetrix</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-2">Performance analysis tool that combines PageSpeed and YSlow recommendations to give detailed insights into website loading speed and optimization opportunities.</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-orange-300">Learn more →</div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/lookup/wappalyzer-alternative" class="square-card transition-all hover:bg-neutral-700 flex flex-col justify-between text-pretty">
                        <div>
                            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                                <div class="square-card border-purple-800 p-1 aspect-square w-10 h-10 object-contain flex items-center justify-center bg-[#460FAD]">
